<li><a href="http://www.sensesofcinema.com/contents/directors/02/tarkovsky.html" class="external text" title="http://www.sensesofcinema.com/contents/directors/02/tarkovsky.html" rel="nofollow">Andrei Tarkovsky</a> at <a href="/wiki/Senses_of_Cinema" title="Senses of Cinema">Senses of Cinema</a></li>
